result.name: California Pizza Kitchen - San Po Kong

reviews.text: The best pizza and pasta place in San Po Kong. Don't go to any other western restaurants in San Po Kong. Coz I haven't found yet... this is a franchise so the taste is kinda guaranteed in a way.

This is my favorite restaurant to get the best pizza after living in NYC for over 14 years. I had the chance to try it in NY, but then there were too many options. Here in Hong Kong tho, I think they make the best one.
The food is actually quite decent, but it's severely understaffed.  Shame on management for not addressing this.
Excellent pizza good deal

Inefficient and missed our order even when there were only 5 tables of people.  Food are sometimes rotten.  It's the problem of this branch only.  CPK branches at TKO and Megabox are good and do not have such problems.

result.formatted_address: 香港新蒲崗太子道東638號
result.name: CALIFORNIA PIZZA KITCHEN - 新蒲崗

reviews.text:
已經光顧了好幾年
食物質素以及環境衛生均退步
最近一次晚市，發現地氈非常污糟，應該很久沒有清潔過，發出一陣酸餿味，希望餐廳正視。
喜歡那裡的套餐，更值得一提小女孩的侍應。由於有一枱的小童嘔吐，地下也弄污了。她小心翼翼收搭枱椅的一切，最後連地下的一片片也一概抹好，非常讚好。
卡位座得好迫，唔夠冷氣，羽衣金蘭，芒果沙律好味，pizza薄啲都好味
The best pizza and pasta place in San Po Kong. Don't go to any other western restaurants in San Po Kong. Coz I haven't found yet... this is a franchise so the taste is kinda guaranteed in a way.
午餐超值之選；汽水檸茶任飲，又多選擇
